I move amendment No. 1:
In page 8, between lines 6 and 7, to insert the following:" "Act of 1994" means the Maternity Protection Act 1994;
"Act of 1995” means the Adoptive Leave Act 1995;".This is a technical amendment required in order to provide additional definitions and interpretations of key terms used throughout the Bill. It is also to clarify the intended scope of the application of the Bill to certain existing enactments.
